code: private static List<Dependency> extractDependenciesFromModel(Model model) {     List<Dependency> dependencies = new ArrayList<>().     for (org.apache.maven.model.Dependency mavenDependency : model.getDependencyManagement().getDependencies()) {         List<Exclusion> exclusions = new ArrayList<>().         for (org.apache.maven.model.Exclusion mavenExclusion : mavenDependency.getExclusions()) {             exclusions.add(new Exclusion(mavenExclusion.getGroupId(), mavenExclusion.getArtifactId())).         }         Dependency dependency = new Dependency(mavenDependency.getGroupId(), mavenDependency.getArtifactId(), mavenDependency.getVersion(), exclusions).         dependencies.add(dependency).     }     return dependencies. }
@Override public Dependency find(String artifactId) {     return this.byArtifactId.get(artifactId). }
